00:35:46.194 --> 00:35:47.732
<font color="#ffffff">(Magdalena Martullo-Blocher)</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Und dann, was passiert?</font>

644
00:35:48.374 --> 00:35:50.422
<font color="#ffffff">Und genau in diesen Branchen,</font>
